罚球拿到 1 分。最终，篮网击败雄鹿迎来新赛季首胜。 10 月 28 日讯 NBA 常规赛，篮网主场击败雄鹿，比赛最后时刻崔永熙获得上场机会，完成了 NBA 正赛首秀！ 据统计，这是自 2018 年 10 月 31 日的周琦以来，首次有中国球员在 NBA 正赛中登场！ 2018 年 10 月 31 日，火箭对阵开拓者，周琦上场 57 秒，1 投 1 中拿下 2 分。 崔永熙首秀 1 分 托马斯 32+5 字母哥 22+12+7 篮网擒鹿迎首胜"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ae5062de0a78da98ce8618e15a776a28_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "99 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2311047736"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIycOrj9DHjt5iEAMaCTExMTQzOTA0NSDWu/u4BjAAOCtAA3IKMjMxMTA0NzczNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1730119549.151536", "card_id": "Q_20914932", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 154}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么成为一个会玩的人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "感觉自己太闷了，不好玩。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ec01b8545f4e21e27f534ba2a4f0a095_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/20914932"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIycOrj9DHjt5iEAMaBjU0NjQ4NSDip/WKBTAAOJBXQARyCDIwOTE0OTMyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1730119549.151772", "card_id": "Q_1052285838", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你印象最深的马拉松是哪次？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "详细谈谈吧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e4383086a46751700e2d225f395248b_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area":